#~ msgstr "De plus Ekos fournit deux outils pour mesurer et corriger l'alignement polaire :"

#, no-c-format
#~ msgid "<guilabel>Polar Alignment Assistant Tool</guilabel>: A very easy tool to measure and correct polar errors. It takes three images near the celestial pole (Close to Polaris for Northern Hemisphere) and then calculates the offset between the mount axis and polar axis."
